377
00:29:09,444 --> 00:29:10,805
<i>Hei, ini menyebalkan.</i>

378
00:29:10,805 --> 00:29:11,805
<i>Aish.</i>

379
00:29:11,805 --> 00:29:13,575
<i>Kau ingat siapa Si Hyun?</i>

380
00:29:13,575 --> 00:29:15,345
<i>Dia tidak seburuk yang kaupikirkan.</i>

381
00:29:15,345 --> 00:29:16,645
<i>Berapa lama lagi
kau akan mengikutiku?</i>

382
00:29:16,645 --> 00:29:17,815
<i>Kenapa kau menelepon
dua hari yang lalu?</i>

383
00:29:17,815 --> 00:29:19,385
<i>Kalau mau tahu,
kau boleh meneleponku.</i>

384
00:29:19,514 --> 00:29:21,155
<i>Apa lagi?
Kau mengikutiku sepanjang jalan sini.</i>

385
00:29:21,155 --> 00:29:22,184
<i>Aku merindukanmu.</i>

386
00:29:22,184 --> 00:29:23,754
<i>Kenapa kau merindukanku?</i>

387
00:29:23,984 --> 00:29:25,254
<i>Aku tertarik padamu.</i>

